    <!-- Privacy -->
    <string name="privacy_title">Privacy policy</string>
    <string name="privacy_body">Outfitly respects your privacy. This policy explains how we handle your data.\n\n1. Data we process\nThe photos you choose or capture are used to generate try-on images. Photos are sent to our AI service for processing and returning the result.\n\n2. Storage\nWe do not store your photos long-term; they are processed only temporarily to create the result. Result images are saved to your device gallery only when you tap Save.\n\n3. Permissions\nThe app requests Camera (to take photos) and Photos access (to pick and save images). You may decline and still use other features.\n\n4. Third parties\nPhotos are processed by our AI service to create try-on results. We do not sell your personal data.\n\n5. Children\nThe app is not directed to children under 13.\n\n6. Contact\nFor any questions, contact us at: exostudio24@gmail.com\n\n7. Changes\nThis policy may be updated over time. Please review it periodically.</string>

